Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What's with you guys?!\NTell me the reason at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who'd like to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits who attacked\NIceberg-san last night were...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from your gang, weren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg was attacked?\NWhat're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:01:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D... Don't be ridiculous! Why...\NWhy would we do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd play innocent to the end, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we really didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Iceberg-san came around, he told\Nus that he remembered the two culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One was a big man with a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other was a tall woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we asked the government,\Nthey said that she's one of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin, the woman\Nwith a bounty on her head!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to this island in order\Nto kill Iceberg-san from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you decide to do so after\Nyou guys met him yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you pirates think...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but now that we've come to know you're\Nthe culprits, we won't leave you at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's one of the culprits?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't forgive him!\NWe definitely can't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, so did Iceberg die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven forbid that he'd\Nget killed by fools like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely because he's still alive,\Nthis guy could go after his life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll take care of him right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead or alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't care if you're captured alive or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what it means\Nto be on the wanted list?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pirates can't complain,\Nno matter who does what to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the world's\Nlaws won't protect you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are outlaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't say things like that when\Nyou know nothing about Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:05.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:08.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:12.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:20.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:30.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:38.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:44.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:52.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:59.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:03.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:10.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:17.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:21.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:25.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:37.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:45.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:55.03,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Straw Hat Pirates Are the Culprits?\NThe Protectors of the City of Water"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he was mistaken!\NThere's no way it was Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we let you get closer\Nwhen we don't know what you'd do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! Tie up the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They tried to kill our town's hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send them to the gallows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You were with that Straw\NHat guy earlier, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be one of them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's right! I saw her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! I said let go\Nof me! What did we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play innocent! You bastards are assassins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you shoot Iceberg-san?!\NWe won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it, you guys!\NWe're saying we didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, Robin doesn't have a reason\Nto go after Iceberg-san, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep insisting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this is it for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn that harming Iceberg-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means that you're turning us,\NGalley-La Company, into an enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you're turning this city,\NWater Seven, into an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying\Ngroundless things like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up, pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The information will spread\Nthroughout this town immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no longer a place for you to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring down everyone in your gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him up, Galley-La Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've only been defending.\NDon't you wanna fight back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I don't have any reason to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now know that pistols don't work on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. Looks like they're\Nall serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--All right! They got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Just as you'd expect from our\Npride and joy, Galley-La Company! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. A guy like that should be blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, that Straw Hat shorty\Nis the Franky Family's detestable enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who was fighting him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you come and snatch\Nmy prey when I'm fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many times do I have\Nto repeat myself, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-Laaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on a sec. We'll deal with\Nyou after we capture him completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said... why in the hell\Nare you capturing my prey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind. Seems like you\Nguys don't get what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-La! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky is gonna launch a crazy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecter set...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought down a huge crane\Nearlier with the same attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brought down a crane?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Get them, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not gonna shoot a cannonball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'll shoot out is an air bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But its speed exceeds the speed of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like high-pressure winds crashed into us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another crane is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! It'll reach this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shipyard like this should be... crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?! A cyborg? Where did\Nhe get that kind of technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was that weird cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to escape thanks to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'd get brought down\Nby something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see Ice pops somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We're going?! It's not\Npossible in this commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! Straw Hat is getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:13:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They got away!\N--Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Maybe he still can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wouldn't be good if\Nwe go closer and he finds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I heard that a storm surge\Ncalled Aqua Laguna is approaching!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! This town will be\Nsubmerged by midnight tonight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shore will be totally submerged, too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!! We shouldn't\Nstay around here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We shouldn't stay around here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry up and\Nevacuate to high ground!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!! Let's hurry up and evacuate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Evacuate!! Evacuate!!\N--Evacuate!! Evacuate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate!! Evacuate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were those voices just now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were saying something\Nabout a storm surge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it... the wind is awfully strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got away. Don't you\Nhave to go after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I ran out fuel with the\NCoupe de Vent I just shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my ducktail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It looks like a\Nwillow swaying in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those damn bastards got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm done refueling,\NI'll eliminate him for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from a man with\Na 100 million bounty on his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is a man of mettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky has really done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible day today is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we can't let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is coming tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for the two sea train\Ndepartures left today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they have no means to leave this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since they can no longer\Nuse the ship they came on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have every Galley-La craftsman\Nspread around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna settle this before sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Grandma! It's Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful not to get too\Nexcited and fall into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the Galley-La\NCompany's main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's connected to Dock #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who look like reporters are all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shipwright-looking people\Nare gathered there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san must be in that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ask Ice pops in person why\Nhe said Robin was one of the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember that we're also being\Nchased after by the entire island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get some idea\Nwhere his room is beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and seize an opportunity to carefully sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:18:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--They said they couldn't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... He is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The window got broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy has broken into the main office!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! In the middle of the day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he attacks the\Nmain office again out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to the mezzanine\Nstairs to the third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are the foremen?!\N--They're stationing craftsmen all\Nover the island, so they're all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing a red vest and a straw hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:19:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't shoot a pistol!\NWe're inside, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good for Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the\Ncommotion outside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that Straw Hat Luffy\Nhas broken into this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa... I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There he is!\N--Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! So many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to Building #2!\NGo around from upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa-san, didn't a pirate come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he didn't. More importantly,\Nchase after him more quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san still needs to rest quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Straw Hat\Nhasn't reached this far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stand watch around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His target is definitely this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you wanted to see me...\Nright, pirate lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Thanks for\Ncalling me in. That saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you came all the way here by\Nyourself to kill me in this commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to hear the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I saw Nico Robin with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... she is one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words no longer mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Nico Robin again now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits for Mr. Iceberg's\Nattack were the Straw Hat pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, Water-Water Newspaper, will buy\Nany information on their sightings!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits are on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the Straw Hats and send\Nthem all to the gallows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be a mistake that\NRobin is the assassin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Craftsmen are everywhere on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that a crazy storm is approaching, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Robin really betrayed--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eternal Farewell? Nico Robin,\Nthe Woman Who Draws Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
